{"tid":763403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"妙齡女墮崖 同行男友人竟稱「我要返工走先」","createTime":"2018-08-01T05:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T14:23:56.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"319c603739e5bd111141b4038d849c786dfcc4af","tid":763403,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:44:53.000Z","msg":"澳洲陽光海岸23歲女子懷利（Sarah Wylie），上周五（27日）應一名大學男同學邀約，一同登山。詎料初次約會竟成噩夢，懷利不慎墮入山谷，男友人竟然拋下一句「上班要遲到了」便急急離去，最終懷利由另外4名行山客救起。<br />\n<br />\n懷利與男伴相約到玻璃屋山國家公園（Glass House Mountains）的汀伯喀登山（Mount Tibrogargan）登高。期間她不慎踩到鬆脫的石塊失足墮山；她反射性抱住一棵樹，惟手部卻遭樹枝嚴重劃傷。<br />\n<br />\n所幸事發時現場恰巧有4名行山客經過，其中3人為消防員，立刻施救。懷利的約會對象眼見有人伸出援手，在消防員替懷利急救時指自己「上班要遲到了」，便獨自離去。事件引發網民熱議，懷利對此大感驚訝，同時呼籲群眾捐款予澳洲的緊急救援隊（SES）。懷利在上周六（28日）接受手術，手上縫了多針，並無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n事後，身兼攀石家的木匠尼克（Nick）邀請懷利一同登山約會，但礙於傷勢，懷利暫未能參與戶外活動。其中一名救人的消防員再次拔刀相助，向他們送贈演唱會門票。尼克則保證，要是懷利在演唱會中摔倒受傷的話，自己絕不會丟下她離去。"},{"pid":"66288b8ea72069414042eb8139731db8a501d034","tid":763403,"uid":12404,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/204541_e6369ed3cfb5ae8ff76dbf63008b76fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F204541_e6369ed3cfb5ae8ff76dbf63008b76fd.jpg&h=ed05ab36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個鬼佬？"},{"pid":"a78c36fd0a70acdf69b7d58f45b071b8d13fba06","tid":763403,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想幫都唔好用呢個借口啦"},{"pid":"a4860eba99d2184e5f3e331ffcbff4f194e81bbd","tid":763403,"uid":38668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"係咪港豬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f38a1038b3a4613b39ee02043fd4e9a0a81cd1","tid":763403,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"條女咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93bc095b5ee3c2b51b4e307c6bd93d804f49168","tid":763403,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"白雪"},{"pid":"60046b768b26060605b7ddf28115abbb148e73f8","tid":763403,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f38a1038b3a4613b39ee02043fd4e9a0a81cd1","tid":763403,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"條女咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"princejoyce咁樣"},{"pid":"8076e2dcbd36f54f718e56982d3f27241119d7db","tid":763403,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:23:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.news.com.au/lifestyle/real-life/news-life/sunshine-coast-woman-rescued-from-the-notorious-mt-tibrogargan-after-horror-fall/news-story/3a6767104dec862418731387d31bb4ae\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Flifestyle%2Freal-life%2Fnews-life%2Fsunshine-coast-woman-rescued-from-the-notorious-mt-tibrogargan-after-horror-fall%2Fnews-story%2F3a6767104dec862418731387d31bb4ae&d=ZFab1yvFwGy4D4nQLMuikDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a5454b9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.com.au/lifestyle/real-life/news-life/sunshine-coast-woman-rescued-from-the-notorious-mt-tibrogargan-after-horror-fall/news-story/3a6767104dec862418731387d31bb4ae</a>"}]}